document.full_text: a 56 year-old canadian woman stranded in a van for seven weeks on a remote dirt road in northern nevada survived on snow and some trail mix until hunters discovered her, authorities said on saturday.
document.title: canadian woman survives 7 weeks lost in remote area of nevada
